{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416800/extras/CONE_PUNK_ABOUT-616-300.jpg?t=1735100708\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cone Punk</strong> is a thrilling 2D platformer that combines action, adventure, and challenging gameplay with a unique visual style. Set in a colorful, post-apocalyptic world, <strong>Cone Punk</strong> invites you to embark on a fast-paced journey where precision platforming and quirky puzzles await.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The characters in <strong>Cone Punk</strong> are brought to life using 3D stop-motion techniques, giving them a distinctive, handcrafted look as they transition into a beautifully animated 2D world. This innovative approach creates a playful, artistic atmosphere that complements the game's quirky humor and immersive environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play solo or join a friend in local couch co-op mode as you jump, dash, and battle through whimsical worlds, unlocking hidden secrets, mastering challenging obstacles, and facing off against unique enemies. Whether you're solving puzzles or competing in multiplayer, <strong>Cone Punk</strong> delivers a fun, skill-based adventure full of creativity.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735100708","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416800/page.bg.jpg?t=1735100708","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416800/3afddf3e1a8a3472c5b47bbe1950e4bb272383af/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735100708","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416800/3afddf3e1a8a3472c5b47bbe1950e4bb272383af/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735100708","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"descri